if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114cae89337952fba43dca70557765d97cc92f4b","tid":249554,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T19:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點正視<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下面咁撚大行字你都可以睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你覺得係現今香港會做到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔做又話唔理唔做  落手推個陣又話點會做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e5950686cbcc852fe44896497b2e36105c0fda","tid":249554,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T19:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點正視<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下面咁撚大行字你都可以睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你覺得係現今香港會做到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔做又話唔理唔做  落手推個陣又話點會做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做又屌唔做又屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3b8fd5f0ba82bf7e0888226d6fcd3aa7d9d466","tid":249554,"uid":55597,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T19:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點正視<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下面咁撚大行字你都可以睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你覺得係現今香港會做到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔做又話唔理唔做  落手推個陣又話點會做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做又屌唔做又屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為呆伯特法則<br />\n<br />\n一些事沒人做，<br />\n一些人沒事做。<br />\n沒事的人盯着做事的人，<br />\n議論做事的人做的事，<br />\n使做事的人做不成事、做不好事。<br />\n<br />\n於是，<br />\n老闆誇獎沒事的人，<br />\n因為他看到事做不成。<br />\n<br />\n於是，<br />\n老闆訓誡做事的人，<br />\n因為他做不成事。<br />\n<br />\n一些沒事的人總是沒事做，<br />\n一些做事的人總有做不完的事。<br />\n一些沒事的人滋事鬧事，<br />\n使做事的人不得不做更多的事。<br />\n<br />\n結果<br />\n好事變壞事，<br />\n小事變大事，<br />\n簡單的事變複雜的事。<br />\n<br />\n然後公司開始出事，<br />\n為了解決這些事，<br />\n老闆開始要求不做事的人做些事，<br />\n<br />\n這些人才做一點點事，<br />\n就到處說他做了全天下最難的事，<br />\n也有人啥事也不做，<br />\n只會光說這是一件不可能成功的事。<br />\n<br />\n最後做事的人還是不得不接下這些沒人做的事，<br />\n公司得救了，<br />\n不做事的人就說：<br />\n那還不是開頭做了許多事，<br />\n公司再見了，<br />\n他們也說：<br />\n我早說那是不可能的事。<br />\n<br />\n最後全公司的人都不做事，<br />\n反正不做事也不會出事，<br />\n多做事反而會惹事。<br />\n<br />\n阿拉伯諺語：<br />\n「你若不想做，會找到一個藉口。<br />\n你若想做，會找到一個方法」"},{"pid":"f92bac5f9ed2f12efcc1ae7c651471ba606f0c13","tid":249554,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37eb9f11f27372f44077fd2f52633d298c6f01c3","tid":249554,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:11:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd14df218c0312b6bc09cec3fb109a0dff7a5914","tid":249554,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T23